---
layout: base.njk
title: "Apartments near Muskegon, MI | Mona Shores Flats — Norton Shores"
description: "Brand-new 1–3 bedroom apartments in Norton Shores, MI. Mona Shores schools, Mona Lake access, in-unit laundry, granite, pet friendly. From $1,425/mo. Tour today."
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero__media">
    <img src="/img/building.jpg" alt="Mona Shores Flats apartment building exterior" fetchpriority="high">
  </div>
  <div class="hero__inner wrap">
    <div class="hero__tags">
      <span class="tag tag--solid">Now Leasing · Muskegon Area</span>
      <span class="tag tag--ghost">🎉 One Month Free · Summer Move-In Special</span>
    </div>
    <h1>Brand-new living,<br>steps from Mona Lake.</h1>
    <p class="hero__sub">1–3 bedroom apartments in Norton Shores — Mona Shores schools, in-unit laundry, granite kitchens, and a private balcony. From $1,425/mo.</p>
    <div class="hero__actions">
      <a class="btn btn--light btn--lg" href="/contact/#tour">Schedule a Tour</a>
      <a class="btn btn--ghost btn--lg" style="color:#fff;border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.5)" href="{{ site.urls.availability }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Check Live Availability →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="stats">
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat__n">2025</div><div class="stat__l">New Construction</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat__n">$1,425</div><div class="stat__l">Starting / mo</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat__n">1 Mo Free</div><div class="stat__l">Move-In Special</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat__n">1–3 BR</div><div class="stat__l">Floor Plans</div></div>
</div>

<!-- Intro -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="split" data-reveal>
      <div class="split__media"><img src="/img/living.jpg" alt="Light-filled apartment living room"></div>
      <div class="stack">
        <div class="eyebrow">Norton Shores, MI</div>
        <h2>Five minutes from Muskegon. A short walk from the water.</h2>
        <div class="points" style="margin-top:18px">
          <div class="point"><h3>Steps from Mona Lake</h3><p>695 acres connected to Lake Michigan — the park, the shoreline, and the water are your everyday backyard.</p></div>
          <div class="point"><h3>Mona Shores School District</h3><p>Among the best-rated in West Michigan. Establish your address while you settle in.</p></div>
          <div class="point"><h3>Everything new in 2025</h3><p>In-unit washer/dryer, granite, stainless, private balcony — move in and live, no surprises.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Location / lifestyle band — swap /img/building.jpg for a drone/aerial shot when available -->
<section class="locband" data-reveal>
  <div class="locband__media"><img src="/img/building.jpg" alt="Mona Shores Flats in Norton Shores, minutes from Mona Lake and the Lake Michigan shoreline" loading="lazy"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="locband__box">
      <div class="eyebrow" style="color:#cfe0ea">The Neighborhood</div>
      <h2>Minutes from the lakeshore.</h2>
      <p>Brand-new in Norton Shores, with Mona Lake and the Lake Michigan shoreline just down the road. Mona Shores schools, shopping and restaurants next door, and a playground for the kids — a cool, quiet corner of West Michigan to call home. In the area? Come check us out.</p>
      <div class="hero__actions" style="margin-top:18px">
        <a class="btn btn--light btn--lg" href="/neighborhood/">Explore the area →</a>
        <a class="btn btn--ghost btn--lg" style="color:#fff;border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.5)" href="/contact/#tour">Schedule a Tour</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Floor plans preview -->
<section class="section section--alt">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section__head" data-reveal>
      <div class="stack"><div class="eyebrow">Floor Plans</div><h2>Find your fit.</h2></div>
      <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/floor-plans/">All floor plans →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="grid plans">
      {% for p in site.floorplans %}
      <a class="plan" href="/floor-plans/{{ p.slug }}/" data-reveal>
        <div class="plan__media"><img src="{{ p.img }}" alt="{{ p.name }} apartment" loading="lazy"></div>
        <div class="plan__body">
          <div class="plan__label">{{ p.name }}{% if p.accessible %}<span class="badge">ADA</span>{% endif %}</div>
          <div class="plan__price">${{ p.price }}<span>/mo · {{ p.sqft }} sq ft</span></div>
          <div class="plan__meta">{{ p.beds }} bed · {{ p.baths }} bath</div>
          <div class="plan__foot">
            <span class="btn btn--accent btn--block">View details →</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- What's included -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section__head" data-reveal>
      <div class="stack">
        <div class="eyebrow">What's Included</div>
        <h2>What's included?</h2>
        <p class="lead">A brand-new 2025 community where the everyday extras come standard. Take a look inside.</p>
      </div>
      <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/amenities/">All amenities →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="acards" data-reveal>
      <figure class="acard"><img src="/img/kitchen.jpg" alt="Granite island kitchen" loading="lazy"><figcaption class="acard__label"><strong>Granite Kitchens</strong><span>Island layouts · stainless</span></figcaption></figure>
      <figure class="acard"><img src="/img/gym.jpg" alt="On-site fitness center" loading="lazy"><figcaption class="acard__label"><strong>Fitness Center</strong><span>Cardio · strength · Peloton</span></figcaption></figure>
      <figure class="acard"><img src="/img/laundry.jpg" alt="In-unit washer and dryer" loading="lazy"><figcaption class="acard__label"><strong>In-Unit Laundry</strong><span>Full-size W/D</span></figcaption></figure>
      <figure class="acard"><img src="/img/courtyard.jpg" alt="Private balcony with French doors" loading="lazy"><figcaption class="acard__label"><strong>Private Balconies</strong><span>Off every living area</span></figcaption></figure>
      <figure class="acard"><img src="/img/bathroom.jpg" alt="Granite bathroom vanity" loading="lazy"><figcaption class="acard__label"><strong>Granite Baths</strong><span>Modern fixtures</span></figcaption></figure>
      <figure class="acard"><img src="/img/living2.jpg" alt="Open-concept living area" loading="lazy"><figcaption class="acard__label"><strong>Open Living</strong><span>High ceilings · bright</span></figcaption></figure>
    </div>
    <div class="incl" data-reveal>
      {% for c in site.community %}
      <div class="incl__item"><strong>{{ c.name }}</strong><span>{{ c.note }}</span></div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Gallery teaser -->
<section class="section section--alt">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section__head" data-reveal>
      <div class="stack"><div class="eyebrow">Gallery</div><h2>Take a look inside.</h2></div>
      <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/gallery/">View full gallery →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="grid" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)" data-reveal>
      {% for g in [site.gallery[1], site.gallery[3], site.gallery[5]] %}
      <a href="/gallery/" class="teaser-tile" style="display:block;border-radius:var(--r-md);overflow:hidden;aspect-ratio:4/3"><img src="{{ g.src }}" alt="{{ g.cap }}" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover"></a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Testimonials -->
{% if site.testimonials.length %}
<section class="section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section__head" data-reveal>
      <div class="stack"><div class="eyebrow">Resident Reviews</div><h2>People love living here.</h2></div>
      {% if site.googleReviewsUrl %}<a class="btn btn--ghost" href="{{ site.googleReviewsUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Read Google reviews →</a>{% endif %}
    </div>
    <div class="grid quotes">
      {% for t in site.testimonials %}
      <figure class="quote" data-reveal>
        <div class="quote__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <blockquote class="quote__text">"{{ t.quote }}"</blockquote>
        <figcaption class="quote__who">— {{ t.name }}</figcaption>
      </figure>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% if site.googleReviewsUrl %}
    <div class="reviews-cta" data-reveal>
      <strong>Loved your visit?</strong>
      <span class="muted" style="font-size:.9rem">Reviews help other renters find us.</span>
      <a class="btn btn--accent" style="margin-left:auto" href="{{ site.googleReviewsUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Leave a Google review →</a>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

<!-- Inline tour scheduler -->
<section class="section section--alt" id="book">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="split">
      <div class="stack">
        <div class="eyebrow">Book in 30 Seconds</div>
        <h2>Ready to see it?</h2>
        <p class="lead">Leave your info and we'll follow up the same day to set up your tour — no obligation. Ready now? You can apply online in minutes.</p>
        <ul class="feature__list" style="margin-top:8px">
          <li>Tours 7 days a week — in person or live video</li>
          <li>One month free on summer move-ins</li>
          <li><a href="{{ site.urls.apply }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--accent);font-weight:600">Skip the wait — apply online →</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      {% set funnelId = "book-form" %}
      {% include "tour-funnel.njk" %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="section cta">
  <div class="wrap stack center">
    <h2>Units are going fast.</h2>
    <p>{{ site.special }} Lock in your floor plan now.</p>
    <div class="cta__actions">
      <a class="btn btn--light btn--lg" href="/contact/#tour">Schedule a Tour</a>
      <a class="btn btn--accent btn--lg" href="{{ site.urls.apply }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apply Now →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% block scripts %}
<script src="/assets/js/funnel.js" defer></script>
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "ApartmentComplex",
  "name": "Mona Shores Flats",
  "url": "{{ site.url }}/",
  "telephone": "+1-616-737-8592",
  "image": "{{ site.url }}/img/building.jpg",
  "numberOfAccommodationUnits": 120,
  "petsAllowed": true,
  "yearBuilt": 2025,
  "address": { "@type": "PostalAddress", "streetAddress": "{{ site.address.street }}", "addressLocality": "{{ site.address.city }}", "addressRegion": "{{ site.address.region }}", "postalCode": "{{ site.address.zip }}", "addressCountry": "US" },
  "geo": { "@type": "GeoCoordinates", "latitude": {{ site.address.lat }}, "longitude": {{ site.address.lng }} }
}
</script>
{% endblock %}
